{"id":261,"parent_id":260,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":261,"title":"2 John 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"2 Jn.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1","content":[["div",[".title","The Second Epistle of",["br"],["span.dominant","John"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","John rejoices because the children of the elect lady are true and faithful."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.1","order":"03.26.001.26853"},["b","1"],"The elder unto the elect lady and her children, whom I love in the truth; and not I only, but also all they that have known the truth;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.2","order":"03.26.001.26854"},["b","2"],"For the truth’s sake, which dwelleth in us, and shall be with us for ever."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.3","order":"03.26.001.26855"},["b","3"],"Grace be with you, mercy,",["i","and"],"peace, from God the Father, and from the Lord Jesus Christ, the Son of the Father, in truth and love."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.4","order":"03.26.001.26856"},["b","4"],"I rejoiced greatly that I found of thy children walking in truth, as we have received a commandment from the Father."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.5","order":"03.26.001.26857"},["b","5"],"And now I beseech thee, lady, not as though I wrote a new commandment unto thee, but that which we had from the beginning, that we love one another."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.6","order":"03.26.001.26858"},["b","6"],"And this is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"love"],", that we",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"walk"],"after his commandments. This is the commandment, That, as ye have heard from the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_6c"},"beginning"],", ye should walk in it."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.7","order":"03.26.001.26859"},["b","7"],"For many",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"deceivers"],"are entered into the world, who confess not that Jesus Christ is come in the flesh. This is a deceiver and an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"antichrist"],"."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.8","order":"03.26.001.26860"},["b","8"],"Look to yourselves, that we lose not those things which we have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"wrought"],", but that we receive a full reward."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.9","order":"03.26.001.26861"},["b","9"],"Whosoever transgresseth, and abideth not in the doctrine of Christ, hath not God. He that abideth in the doctrine of Christ, he hath both the Father and the Son."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.10","order":"03.26.001.26862"},["b","10"],"If there come any unto you, and bring not this doctrine, receive him not into",["i","your"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"house"],", neither bid him God speed:"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.11","order":"03.26.001.26863"},["b","11"],"For he that biddeth him God speed is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"partaker"],"of his evil deeds."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.12","order":"03.26.001.26864"},["b","12"],"Having many things to write unto you, I would not",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"write"]],"with paper and ink: but I trust to come unto you, and speak face to face, that our joy may be full."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.13","order":"03.26.001.26865"},["b","13"],"The children of thy elect sister greet thee. Amen."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.6a","order":"03.26.001.26866"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/family-love-within"},"TG Family, Love within"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.6b","order":"03.26.001.26868"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/walking-with-god"},"TG Walking with God"],"."],["div",{"id":"6c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.6c","order":"03.26.001.26870"},["b","6c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/2.24"},"1 Jn. 2:24"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.7a","order":"03.26.001.26872"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/deceit"},"TG Deceit"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.7b","order":"03.26.001.26874"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/antichrist"},"TG Antichrist"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.8a","order":"03.26.001.26876"},["b","8a"],["span.small","GR"],"performed, acquired."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.10a","order":"03.26.001.26878"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/5.11"},"1 Cor. 5:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.11a","order":"03.26.001.26880"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/5.22"},"1 Tim. 5:22"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/2-jn/1.12a","order":"03.26.001.26882"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/scriptures-writing-of"},"TG Scriptures, Writing of"],"."]]}
